bin">∧</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">敲</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">声</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">沉</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">闷</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mclose">]</span></span></span></span></span></p>
