ht:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">清</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">脆</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">和</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">色</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">泽</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">乌</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">黑</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mbin">∧</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">根</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">蒂</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">硬</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">挺</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mbin">∧</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">敲</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">声</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">沉</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">闷</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p>​		都分类为&quot;好瓜&quot;。若使用最多包含k个合取式的析合范式来表达表1.1西瓜分类问题的假设控件，试估算共有多少种可能的假设。</p>
